We have created a website name Zee5.
This Website is for entertainment purposes so you can watch
your favorite movies, shows, and news from anywhere.
when you click on our website you will reach the Homepage.
from here you can access the videos 
there are some pages we attach to our navbar so you can  easily find 
the genre you want to watch.
if you want to see some movies, tv shows, web series, or  news
you can directly click on the above respective pages.
when you click on some poster you can see some buttons there,
there is a watch button option from here you can watch your favorite videos
by clicking on it.
if you want to go to the premium plans there you can see
a buy plan button by clicking on it you will land on that page
Here you can buy plans by clicking on the continue button.
after the process, you have to go through the login process
by clicking on the login button  the login page will be visible 
here you have to log in if you have registered before
if not then you have to register first.
after clicking on register you have to enter your
the number after that you will receive some OTP after entering the correct OTP
you will receive a pop message on the screen,
after successful signup then you have to go the
login part, you have to enter your registered mobile number
in the login page and after verifying you will 
receive another OTP, enter the OTP correctly
you will receive another pop-up message on the screen written 
login successful. your login process is done here
in the end, you can find some help center page where we
will solve your queries and you can also reach us by clicking on about us 
page, in the bottom part you will find our social media handling account.
This is all about the functionality we have added to our website.
Thank you for visiting our website.
